name: Wing Warriors
overview: Here comes the arcade shooter WING WARRIORS. This is the story about three great Wing Warriors (Kai, Gaia and Raiden) who are in fight with the Black Emperor. Enjoy this game with successful air combats. Top quality graphics and sound. Hordes of enemies and different weapons. 3 long levels, 3 deadly bosses. Three characters following epic storylines. Select your character and begin the wonderful combats of WING WARRIORS. Prepare for battle!
